POWERCOM CO LTD (3043)  said unconsolidated sales
in May fell 52.01% to NT$164,065,000 from NT$341,885,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  5/2012           5/2011
Sales            164,065          341,885    
YOY%             -52.01%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales            754,355         2,160,114   
YOY%             -65.08% 
=================================================================
 